---
/**
 * Hero section — honest positioning as a solo AI engineer
 */
---

<section class="relative overflow-hidden">
  <div
    class="absolute -top-32 -left-32 w-[480px] h-[480px] bg-indigo-500/10 blur-3xl rounded-full pointer-events-none">
  </div>
  <div
    class="absolute -bottom-48 -right-40 w-[520px] h-[520px] bg-blue-500/10 blur-3xl rounded-full pointer-events-none">
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 pt-20 pb-20 md:pt-28 md:pb-28">
    <div class="max-w-3xl">
      <div
        class="inline-flex gap-2 w-max text-xs text-white/80 bg-white/5 border-white/10 border rounded-full mb-5 py-1 px-2.5 backdrop-blur-lg items-center">
        <span class="inline-flex h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-indigo-400"></span>
        Solo engineer, vertical AI focus
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl font-semibold tracking-tight leading-[1.1]">
        Building AI tools for <br class="hidden md:block">
        underserved industries
      </h1>

      <p class="mt-5 text-base sm:text-lg text-white/70 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
        I'm Gabriel Galer. I build AI-powered software for professional domains where
        legacy workflows&mdash;Excel spreadsheets, manual processes, paper forms&mdash;are still the norm.
        7 years of full-stack engineering. TypeScript, React, Node, AI agents.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3">
        <a href="/blog"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center h-11 hover:bg-white/90 transition text-sm font-medium text-neutral-900 bg-white rounded-xl px-5 shadow-lg shadow-indigo-500/10">
          Read the blog
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="ml-1.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M5 12h14"></path>
            <path d="M12 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
          </svg>
        </a>
        <a href="#" data-cal-link="octatech/discovery" data-cal-config='{"layout":"month_view"}'
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center h-11 hover:text-white hover:border-white/20 transition text-sm text-white/90 border-white/10 border rounded-xl px-5 backdrop-blur-lg">
          Book a call
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="ml-1.5" fill="none">
            <path
              d="M12 22C17.5228 22 22 17.5228 22 12C22 6.47715 17.5228 2 12 2C6.47715 2 2 6.47715 2 12C2 13.5997 2.37562 15.1116 3.04346 16.4525C3.22094 16.8088 3.28001 17.2161 3.17712 17.6006L2.58151 19.8267C2.32295 20.793 3.20701 21.677 4.17335 21.4185L6.39939 20.8229C6.78393 20.72 7.19121 20.7791 7.54753 20.9565C8.88837 21.6244 10.4003 22 12 22Z"
              fill="currentColor" fill-opacity="0.4" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
